annotationA: Sphingolipid delta-4 desaturase activity; stearoyl-CoA 9-desaturase activity. It is involved in the biological process described with: spermatogenesis; sphingolipid biosynthetic process; spindle assembly involved in male meiosis
annotationB: Alkaline ceramidase; Hydrolyzes the sphingolipid ceramide into sphingosine and free fatty acid
